      <span class="footer-project">虎峰禅寺改扩建项目概念方案初稿</span>
      <img class="footer-logo" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/YUANGOU-LB/HuFeng-Temple@c0388ed/images/img_007.png" alt="原构">
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- S6: 场地高差与利用策略 -->

<div class="slide slide-content" id="s6">
  <div class="slide-inner">
    <div class="slide-header">
      <div class="slide-title">场地高差分析</div>
      <div class="slide-pn">07</div>
      </div>
    <div class="layout-2col text-img">
      <div class="col-text">
<h3>地形特征</h3>
<ul>
<li>地块位于虎峰山靠近山顶的相对平缓区域，整体北高南低，北陡南缓，高差约18m，整体坡度约13%</li>
<li>一期用地位于北部靠近虎峰，南北进深约64m，高差25m，坡度较陡约39%</li>
<li>二期用地位于南部平坦区域，南北进深约74m，高差约3m，坡度约4%</li>
</ul>
</div>
