<div class="slide slide-content" id="s14b">
  <div class="slide-inner">
    <div class="slide-header">
      <div class="slide-title">建筑风格 · 材质色彩</div>
      <div class="slide-pn">34</div>
      </div>
    <div class="layout-2col text-img">
      <div class="col-text">
        <h3>古法唐风</h3>
        <p>延续唐代建筑雄浑、大气、简洁的风格，融合浙东地方特色，体现"古朴雄健"之美。</p>
        <h3>材质与色彩</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><span class="tag">主材</span> 青石柱础台基 + 深色木材梁柱</li>
          <li><span class="tag">屋顶</span> 灰色陶瓦，翼角舒展</li>
          <li><span class="tag">墙体</span> 粉墙，灰白主基调</li>
          <li><span class="tag">色彩</span> 栗色、灰色、青灰色</li>
        </ul>
